content.rendered:
Directed by Mathukutty Xavier

Written by Mathukutty Xavier

Cast Janhvi Kapoor (Mili Naudiyal). Manoj Pahwa (Niranjan Naudiyal). Sunny Kaushal (Sameer Kumar). Deepak Simwal (Vipul). Aryav Agrwal (School Kid Boy). Niranjan Asrani (Security Guard at Mall). Nupur Awasthi (Lady Constable Hema). Dheeraj Batra (Auto Driver). Deepak Bhardwaj (Senior CCTV Guy). Raghav Binani (Laddu). Niharika Chouksey (Piya (Mohan’s Daughter) (as Niharika Chowske)). Sarthak Das (Delivery Boy). Vimla Dhaundiyal (Flower Lady at Shop). Azhar Gaur (Mili’s Friend). Richa Gaur (Anjali’s Mother). Mvayitre Ghoshal (Teacher). Mayank Godiyal (Drunk Bike Rider). Joginder Goyat (Shyam). Khushi Hajare (Young Mili). Mohd Iqbal (Niranjan Dubai Friend). Ravi Karanwal (Auto Driver). Abdullah Khan (Young Warch Man). Shagun Khurana (Mili’s Nursing Friend 2). Vikram Kochhar (Sudhir malkoti). Deepak Kripalani (Doctor). Ajeeta Kulkarni (Sheela Mohan’s Wife). Chandresh Kulshrestha (K.C. Diwedi). Rajendra Kumar (Father of Mili’s Nursing Friend 1). Vishwas Kumar (Father of Kid With Toy). Lovekush Kundu (Auto Romeo (as Auto Romeo)). Rishad Mahmud (Rishad). Sanjay Mahto (Ravi Prasad’s Team). Sanjay Mahto (Constable Hari Sharma). Indreshwari Mamgain (Cleaning Lady 1). Maanav Matalia (Firoz (Sameer’s Friend)). Mayank Mishra (Travel Agency Guy). Nick Nag (Kid With Toy). Nikolay Novomlinsky (Foreigner at Chicken Hub). Hunny Singh Pahwa (Immigration Officer). Rajesh Pandey (Mall Manager). Jay Parashar (Constable Vimal Khatri). Abhishek Patel (Prisoner). Shruti Priya (Mother of Kid Patient). Aryav Rathore (Sameer’s Friend 2). Seema Rawat (Cleaning Lady 2). Anushree Sahu (Mili’s Nursing Friend 1). Shadaab Salmani (Car Guy Accident Scene). Waseem Shaikh (Cinema Hall Romeo). Mukesh Sharma (Old Auto Driver). Jackie Shroff (Adam Latchman (Guest Appearance)). Deepak Singh (Petrol Pump Guy). Micky Singh (Senior Nurse). Shekhar Singh (Shiv (Sameer’s Friend)). Sanjay Suri (Inspector Ravi Prasad). Myrah Talwar (School Kid Girl). Vikas Talwar (Hasleen’s Husband). Kapil Tanwar (Junior CCTV Guy). Manohar Teli (Constable Mukesh Singh). Sunil Thakur (Inspector Satish Rawat). Vivan Thapa (Kid in Hospital). Mayank Tiwari (Travel Agent). Mamta Verma (Mili’s Mother). Kavita Virmani (Sameer’s Mother)

Language Hindi

Producers Boney Kapoor. Yogiraj Shetty. Vikas Talwar. Vinod Talwar. Mayank Tiwari.

Production Bayview Projects. Zee Studios
